00:06:57,512 --> 00:07:01,812
I'm sorry, I'm so thoughtless!

113
00:07:01,812 --> 00:07:04,012
"Mouri Detective Agency"

114
00:07:05,112 --> 00:07:07,412
What's the matter, Conan?

115
00:07:07,412 --> 00:07:09,612
