00:07:41,312 --> 00:07:44,443
Mom nor I got one yet.

130
00:07:45,512 --> 00:07:47,012
Hello there, great detective.

131
00:07:48,112 --> 00:07:51,212
Welcome to Urai Confections 8th Anniversary Party.

132
00:07:51,212 --> 00:07:55,812
Who may I ask are you?

133
00:07:55,812 --> 00:07:59,112
I'm President of Urai Confections, Taruto Urai.

134
00:07:59,112 --> 00:08:01,512
I think we've never met before.

135
00:08:01,512 --> 00:08:03,512
President?

136
00:08:03,512 --> 00:08:07,112
And this is my wife and vice-president.

137
00:08:07,112 --> 00:08:10,469
I'm Hoshie. It's an honor to see you,

138
00:08:10,469 --> 00:08:12,812
Mr. Sleeping Kogoro.

139
00:08:12,812 --> 00:08:15,612
Well, hello.

140
00:08:21,812 --> 00:08:24,483
