141
00:08:24,483 --> 00:08:25,912
Really.

142
00:08:25,912 --> 00:08:27,812
Look at all the people, Conan.

143
00:08:27,812 --> 00:08:28,812
Yeah.

144
00:08:29,912 --> 00:08:31,312
Come along!

145
00:08:31,312 --> 00:08:33,212
It's a buffet,

146
00:08:33,212 --> 00:08:36,912
