Come over here, Ran.

149
00:08:44,512 --> 00:08:46,012
It's all kinds of food all you can eat!

150
00:08:46,012 --> 00:08:47,612
You'd better make yourself a plate right away too!

151
00:08:47,612 --> 00:08:49,212
Fried prawns, fried prawns!

152
00:08:49,212 --> 00:08:50,912
Hey, Dad, hold it.

153
00:08:50,912 --> 00:08:53,212
Pops, control yourself.

154
00:08:55,812 --> 00:08:56,912
It's good!

155
00:08:56,912 --> 00:08:58,517
Just as expected of the Haido City Hotel,

156
00:08:58,712 --> 00:09:00,519
the food is top class too!

157
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:03,212
I wonder what they have in store for us.

158
00:09:03,212 --> 00:09:04,312
What?

159
00:09:04,312 --> 00:09:06,212
It's President Urai!

160
00:09:06,212 --> 00:09:07,812
According to Sonoko,

161
00:09:07,812 --> 00:09:11,512
he does something interesting at every party.

162
00:09:11,512 --> 00:09:13,012
He does magic,

163
00:09:13,012 --> 00:09:15,612
or come out wearing the stuffed animal clothes that he wore on TV ads,

