00:09:32,912 --> 00:09:34,112
Yes.

169
00:09:34,112 --> 00:09:36,912
I'm glad and was right to have used you to make that commercial.

170
00:09:36,912 --> 00:09:38,312
Well, well!

171
00:09:41,012 --> 00:09:44,112
The fact is, I asked Yoko to use you

172
00:09:44,112 --> 00:09:47,812
