202
00:11:17,412 --> 00:11:19,912
Hey! Hey! Hey!

203
00:11:19,912 --> 00:11:22,312
Is it working?

204
00:11:22,312 --> 00:11:24,212
Yes, I'm listening!

205
00:11:24,212 --> 00:11:26,412
No, you.

206
00:11:26,412 --> 00:11:29,012
Yeah, I think so.

207
00:11:30,312 --> 00:11:34,112
But, finally after a dramatic turn of the tables,

208
00:11:34,112 --> 00:11:36,112
you two may become a couple,

209
00:11:36,112 --> 00:11:39,212
so try not to get into too many fights with your boyfriend.

210
00:11:39,212 --> 00:11:40,212
Okay.

211
00:11:52,691 --> 00:11:56,312
Hey, what is it, Dear?

212
00:11:56,312 --> 00:11:59,012
Is this supposed to be your mystery skit?

213
00:12:03,712 --> 00:12:06,705
Detective Mouri, come here, please!

214
00:12:06,705 --> 00:12:09,512
I guess it's showtime for you.

215
00:12:09,512 --> 00:12:11,812
Yes?

216
00:12:11,812 --> 00:12:15,812
