240
00:13:33,937 --> 00:13:37,337
So, when the president collapsed,

241
00:13:37,337 --> 00:13:40,799
Conan, Ran and you, his wife,

242
00:13:41,037 --> 00:13:43,337
who is the vice president of Urai Confections,

243
00:13:43,337 --> 00:13:46,805
were the only three near him?

244
00:13:46,805 --> 00:13:49,337
Yes, that's right.

245
00:13:49,337 --> 00:13:51,637
I think it was just when Mr. Mouri went up to the podium

246
00:13:51,637 --> 00:13:54,037
to deliver his speech.

247
00:13:54,037 --> 00:13:55,237
Yes.

248
00:13:55,237 --> 00:13:58,817
My husband suddenly let out a loud groan and fell to the floor.

249
00:13:59,037 --> 00:14:01,237
He hasn't moved since.

250
00:14:01,237 --> 00:14:02,237
If I remember correctly,

251
00:14:02,237 --> 00:14:06,837
the one who was right beside the president at that time was you.

252
00:14:06,837 --> 00:14:10,829
Yes. I was palm reading for Ran.

253
00:14:10,829 --> 00:14:11,837
Palm reading?

254
00:14:11,837 --> 00:14:13,737
Is it true?

255
00:14:13,737 --> 00:14:14,833
Yes.

256
00:14:14,833 --> 00:14:17,837
Mrs. Urai held my left hand with both her hands

257
00:14:17,837 --> 00:14:19,337
