260
00:14:27,237 --> 00:14:32,037
Did Mrs. Urai call out to her husband back then?

261
00:14:32,037 --> 00:14:34,853
Saying something like drink something or eat something.

262
00:14:34,853 --> 00:14:36,855
No, not especially.

263
00:14:36,855 --> 00:14:39,937
But while she was reading your palm,

264
00:14:39,937 --> 00:14:42,037
Mrs. Urai said at one point,

265
00:14:42,037 --> 00:14:45,537
"Is it working?".

266
00:14:45,537 --> 00:14:47,837
Working?

267
00:14:47,837 --> 00:14:51,137
At first I thought she was talking to me,

268
00:14:51,137 --> 00:14:54,037
